data.description: The residence boasts 4 generously-sized bedrooms and 3.5 elegantly designed bathrooms and a huge loft. Recent upgrades include a fresh coat of paint, new plush carpeting, and modern vanities, further elevating the charm of this remarkable property. Situated in close proximity to esteemed schools, lush parks, scenic bike and walking paths, UC Merced, a cutting-edge state-of-the-art hospital, and a thriving shopping hub, this home is a splendid opportunity not to be overlooked. Don't allow this exceptional offering to escape your grasp. With its prime location providing seamless access to UC Merced, shopping centers, the mall, the hospital, medical offices, top-notch restaurants, an array of recreational amenities, prime fishing spots, and opportunities for boating and water skiing, this is an opportunity you won't want to miss.
